node.hospital_zh: 東區尤德夫人那打素醫院
node.detail_zh: 患者為外傭，過往健康良好。7 月 14 日乘搭菲律賓航空 PR300 初次由菲律賓抵港，由亞洲國際博覽館送院。7 月 13 日開始咳嗽。
node.detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper with good past health. She arrived in Hong Kong via Philippine Airlines flight PR300 from the Philippines on July 14 and was transferred to hospital via the Asia World Expo. She started coughing on July 13.
